OL,3,CCouple appear in Magistrates Court
OL,4,Cafter incident outside Jersey's mosque
OL,6,FA man and woman have appeared in
OL,7,FJersey's Magistrates Court in relation
OL,8,Fto an incident outside the Islamic
OL,9,FCentre in St Helier on Friday, 6 March.
OL,11,FJade Clarke James Hamon, and Tamara
OL,12,FNadine Dubois were charged with
OL,13,Foffences following what police
OL,14,Fdescribed as a 'racially motivated
OL,15,Fincident'.
OL,17,FTamara Dubois pleaded guilty to the
OL,18,Fcommon assault of a 13-year-old girl.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
