OL,3,CCouple appear in Magistrates Court
OL,4,Cafter incident outside Jersey's mosque
OL,6,FMs Dubois also entered not guilty
OL,7,Fpleas to two additional charges of
OL,8,Fcommon assault against different
OL,9,Fpeople.
OL,11,FA further not guilty plea was entered
OL,12,Ffor the joint charge of threatening,
OL,13,Fabusive or disorderly conduct.
OL,15,FSeparately, Jade Hamon pleaded not
OL,16,Fguilty to the joint charge of
OL,17,Fthreatening, abusive or disorderly
OL,18,Fconduct.
