OL,3,CCouple appear in Magistrates Court
OL,4,Cafter incident outside Jersey's mosque
OL,6,FBoth Ms Dubois and Mr Hamon remain on
OL,7,Fconditional bail, and the case has
OL,8,Fbeen referred to the Royal Court,
OL,9,Fwhere they will appear on 12 June.
